data.description: What a wonderful west Norman property in convenient Western View neighborhood. The property has been a rental property but Sellers have done many recent updates/improvements. The range, dishwasher, replaced vanity and faucet in primary bath, and the kitchen faucet in 2018. In 2019 the water heater, the east & south fence replaced the west fence was repaired. In 2020 replaced the toilets and the kitchen disposal. Complete roof replaced and replaced and repaired as needed the gutters, downspouts, windows, screens , window blinds and exterior paint in summer of 2021. It has a nice floorplan with a living room with a fireplace and we bar. The property does have a 179 sq foot enclosed sun room with a split system heating and cooling unit. This room is not being counted in the square footage. It has a good size yard and in really good condition.
